items.name: Inconsistent-Array-Iteration-Order-in-PHP-with-Mixed-Key-Types-4nl4d
items.description: PHP array iteration order with mixed string and integer keys can be unpredictable, leading to inconsistent program behavior. This bug demonstrates how the seemingly random order can cause unexpected outputs, and why you should be mindful of key types when iterating through PHP arrays.
